---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Tagline from '../../components/Tagline.astro';
---

<Layout title="DevOps & Infrastructure - Wellmade" description="Your cloud. Your control. Fully managed. Infrastructure that scales with you.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section-primary py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-accent font-medium mb-4">Services</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-8">DevOps & Infrastructure</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80">
        Your cloud. Your control. Fully managed.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 mt-4">
        Infrastructure shouldn't be a bottleneck. Or a mystery. We build, deploy, and manage cloud infrastructure that scales with you - on your accounts, under your control.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why It Matters -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">Why it matters.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Good infrastructure is invisible. Bad infrastructure is why your app is down at 2am.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We've seen too many projects where infrastructure was an afterthought - duct-taped together, impossible to scale, understood by one person who left six months ago.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-title font-medium">
        We do it right from the start. Repeatable. Documented. Yours.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What It Looks Like -->
  <section class="section-alt py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-12">What it looks like.</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Infrastructure as Code.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Everything scripted, versioned, reproducible. No clicking around in consoles, no "I think I changed something last month."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">CI/CD pipelines.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Push code, it deploys. Automatic testing, staging environments, production releases. No manual steps, no crossed fingers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Monitoring and alerting.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Know when something breaks before your users do. Logs, metrics, dashboards that actually help.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Security and compliance.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Proper access controls. Secrets management. Audit trails. We build for compliance, not as a checkbox.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card md:col-span-2">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Scaling.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Up when you need it, down when you don't. No paying for idle servers, no panic when traffic spikes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Work With -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-12">What we work with.</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-title mb-3">Cloud providers</h3>
          <p class="text-body">AWS, Google Cloud, Azure, Scaleway, OVH, Hetzner - we go where your needs take us.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-title mb-3">Containers & orchestration</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Docker, Kubernetes, managed container services.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-title mb-3">Infrastructure as Code</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Terraform, Pulumi, CloudFormation.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-title mb-3">CI/CD</h3>
          <p class="text-body">GitHub Actions, GitLab CI, Bitbucket Pipelines - whatever fits your workflow.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-title mb-3">Monitoring</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Datadog, Grafana, CloudWatch, Sentry - visibility where it matters.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sovereignty -->
  <section class="section-primary py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Sovereignty when it matters.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Data residency matters to many of our clients. GDPR. Industry regulations. Or just wanting to know where your data lives.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We partner with <a href="https://getonyx.eu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:underline">Onyx</a> for sovereign infrastructure expertise - European clouds, on-premise options, data that stays where you need it.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 font-medium">
        But it's not a religion. We're pragmatic. If AWS is the right answer, we'll say so. If sovereignty is critical, we'll build for it. We help you make the right trade-offs.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What You Get -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">What you get.</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg text-body">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Infrastructure running on your cloud accounts</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Everything documented and scripted - no tribal knowledge</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Deployment pipelines that just work</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Monitoring and alerting configured</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Runbooks for common issues</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>A team that can hand over cleanly - or stick around to manage it</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who It's For -->
  <section class="section-alt py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-title mb-6">Who it's for.</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-body">
            <li>Teams launching new products who want to start right</li>
            <li>Companies with infrastructure debt they need to fix</li>
            <li>Organizations moving to the cloud - or moving between clouds</li>
            <li>Anyone whose "DevOps guy" just left and took all the knowledge</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-title mb-6">Who it's not for.</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-body">
            <li>Projects where security is negotiable</li>
            <li>Clients who want us to "just make it work" without understanding what we're building</li>
            <li>One-time setups with no plan for maintenance</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-title mt-6 font-medium">Infrastructure is ongoing. We can manage it for you, or hand it over properly. But "set and forget" isn't real.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work Together -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">How we work together.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We work in days for projects and setup. Flexible, transparent, no surprises.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-8">
        For ongoing operations, we offer <strong>support and maintenance packages</strong> with various SLA levels - from business hours coverage to 24/7/365. When round-the-clock support is critical, we work with trusted partners to ensure you're always covered.
      </p>
      <a href="/working-with-us" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-semibold hover:text-primary/70 transition-colors group">
        See how we work
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-primary py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Let's build your foundation.</h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-accent transition-colors">
        Get in touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Tagline />
</Layout>
